The '''Plaza de España''' in Seville, [[Wikipedia:Spain|Spain]] was filmed on [[September 13]], [[2000]] for an [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|AOTC]] sequence where Anakin and Padmé arrive on [[Naboo]]. A long discussion was featured in the deleted scenes section of the DVD.

